@startuml
title Container Diagram: AI Edge-to-Cloud System

' --------------------
' Edge Layer
' --------------------
package "Edge Layer" {
  [Edge Application\n(Docker Container)] as Edge
}

' --------------------
' Messaging Layer
' --------------------
package "Messaging Layer" {
  [Zookeeper\n(Docker Container)] as ZK
  [Kafka Broker\n(Docker Container)] as Kafka
}

' --------------------
' Cloud Layer
' --------------------
package "Cloud Layer" {
  [Server Application\n(Docker Container)] as Server
}

' --------------------
' Static container dependencies
' --------------------
Edge --> Kafka : depends on
Server --> Kafka : depends on
Kafka --> ZK : depends on

' --------------------
' Notes
' --------------------
note right of Edge
Runs on an edge device
(Laptop, Raspberry Pi, etc.)
Contains inference logic
and Kafka producer
end note

note right of Server
Runs in cloud / VM
Contains Kafka consumer
and Flask-based API
end note

note right of Kafka
Apache Kafka broker
for asynchronous messaging
end note

note right of ZK
Zookeeper for Kafka
coordination and metadata
end note

@enduml



